nodes.text: The 9th Assault Corps was a Corps within in the Grand Army of the Republic. It served during the Clone Wars between the Galactic Republic and the Separatist Alliance. The corps was under the command of Jedi General Luminara Unduli. It included the 41st Elite, a unit under the command of Clone Commander Gree. This unit was renowned for their overwhelming firepower and offensive tactics. Commander Gree was killed by Jedi Master Yoda when he tried to enforce Order 66. The 41st additionally included Green Company, and the 9th featured Sarlacc Battalion A and Sarlacc Battalion B as subordinate units.
